last_episode_to_air.overview: Will there be a happy ending? Josh and Melissa are presented with a life-changing choice.

name: Schmigadoon!
overview: In this parody of 1940s musicals, backpacking couple Melissa and Josh get trapped in Schmigadoon, a magical town filled with singing and dancing townspeople, and learn they can't leave without finding true love—which they thought they already had.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Josh and Melissa miss the magic they felt in Schmigadoon and in an attempt to return, find themselves in Schmicago—the reimagined world of '60s and '70s musicals.

episodes.name: Schmigadoon!
episodes.overview: Melissa and Josh stumble upon the strange musical town of Schmigadoon—and are shocked to learn they can’t leave until they find true love.

episodes.name: Lovers' Spat
episodes.overview: After realizing that they can't leave together, Josh and Melissa break up and start looking for romance around town.

episodes.name: Cross That Bridge
episodes.overview: When their first flings end in regret, Melissa and Josh agree to a new plan—which he immediately casts aside, prompting her to make a fresh start.

episodes.name: Suddenly
episodes.overview: Melissa grapples with her conflicted feelings for Doc Lopez, rebelling against his archaic ideas, while Josh tries to court Emma the schoolmarm.

episodes.name: Tribulation
episodes.overview: New romances hit roadblocks as Melissa meets someone unexpected and Emma reveals a secret. Mildred seizes a chance to increase her power.

episodes.name: How We Change
episodes.overview: With the election looming, Mildred relentlessly ramps up her campaign. Josh and Melissa face their true feelings for each other. Season finale.

episodes.name: Welcome to Schmicago
episodes.overview: Feeling joyless in the real world, Josh and Melissa attempt to return to Schmigadoon but instead find themselves in the darker world of Schmicago.

episodes.name: Doorway to Where
episodes.overview: As Josh makes a new friend in jail, Melissa hires a lawyer and goes undercover to clear his name.

episodes.name: Bells and Whistles
episodes.overview: While Josh spends time on the run with Topher and the tribe, Melissa explores Schmicago looking for clues and uncovers a family secret.

episodes.name: Something Real
episodes.overview: After Josh and Melissa realize they need to find a happy ending for everyone, they try to make that happen—with unintended consequences.

episodes.name: Famous as Hell
episodes.overview: Convinced they’re well on their way to a happy ending, Josh and Melissa both rocket to fame in Schmicago and get embroiled in a deadly plot.

episodes.name: Over and Done
episodes.overview: Will there be a happy ending? Josh and Melissa are presented with a life-changing choice.
